ng the reputation and integrity of the University. For this reason, final applicants will be asked to undergo a background check. Compensation BCGEU Pay Grid - $27.09 to $30.25 per hour Closes: 15 December, 2023 Kwantlen Polytechnic University Surrey , BC Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
